Title: dnsimg - storing images in txt records
Description: I was intrigued by the idea of storing images in DNS records, and I wanted to test out how effectively images could be stored in DNS records. I've always been interested in TXT records because they seem to be a useful way of storing arbitrary data, and in this blog post I'll discuss how I went from an idea to developing the project into almost a protocol sort of method for storing an image on a domain name.
